error: missing required subcommand; valid subcommands: ⁨record, replay, verify, help⁩

Usage: ⁨spycatcher-harness⁩ <COMMAND>

Commands:
  record  Proxy to upstream and record interactions.
  replay  Replay interactions from a cassette.
  verify  Verify cassette and configuration integrity.
  help    Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help     Print help (see more with '--help')
  -V, --version  Print version
